Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:53.26,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,Jimmy Onishi's 24 Hour Long Interview
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.36,0:01:58.89,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Tonight we'll start with his {\c&H1528D6&\3c&HFFFFFF&}popular performer days.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:03.81,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,After high school, Jimmy started working at a Yoshimoto theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:03.80,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\pos(1049.057,871.005)}Starting as a {\c&H00FFEC&}stagehand{\c&HFFFFFF&},\N Jimmy was able to begin \Nhis life as a performer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:09.84,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\fad(250,100)}Starting at 19, he spent two years as Bonchi Osamu's {\c&H1528D6&}apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:14.64,Staff,,0,0,10,,What happened after you finished your apprenticeship?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:19.46,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,At the time, Sanma-san was asking "Any drivers here?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.53,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,He wanted to hire one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:26.04,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,It just so happened I didn't have a job anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:29.18,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,so I thought, "Alright, I'll become a driver."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:32.41,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,He was 22 at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.78,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,To work as Sanma's driver, he {\c&H1528D6&}headed to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:39.88,Staff,,0,0,10,,How much did you get paid back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:42.52,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Between 200,000 and 300,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:45.48,Staff,,0,0,10,,And how did you spend that money?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:48.94,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Mostly on sex services.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.89,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(349.5,930)}There he goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:52.52,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Well, if I had 300,000, I'd spend 280,000 yen on sex services.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.01,0:02:56.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,10,,Just spend all {\c&H000000&}300,000 yen{\c&H1727D6&} then!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:03:02.20,Title 2 - White,,0,0,10,,Q. How did you get your big break?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:03:02.20,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\pos(693,806)}By being part of "Hyokin zoku" and then "Yatteru Yatteru"
