Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:44.66,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,And so, it's been 11 hours since the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:49.44,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,To change the mood, we go outside for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:52.30,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Of course, while they're on their way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:54.25,Staff,,0,0,10,,What do you like to eat when you go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:57.21,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I like to eat sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:01.30,Staff,,0,0,10,,Do you like ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:01.32,Staff,,0,0,230,,Yeah, I like ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.42,Staff,,0,0,10,,What flavor do you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:06.66,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Soy sauce or salt flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:08.73,Staff,,0,0,10,,So you dislike miso flavor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.73,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Miso flavor is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:14.09,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,It's not that I dislike it, I just don't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:15.52,Hamada,,0,0,10,,You're getting a bit {\c&H000000&}angry.
