Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:32.98,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Right now, I refuse to answer any more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:35.01,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Really, it's been enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:42.17,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Here, we will delve into Jimmy's enigmatic {\c&H00FFF7&}painter days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:42.41,Yamazaki,,0,0,160,,I want to hear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:48.46,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,It was 1996 and Jimmy was one of the most popular comedians, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:50.92,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,he suddenly decided to {\c&H1727D6&}become a painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:56.20,Title 2 - White,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,100)}For what {\c&H1727D6&}reason {\c&HFFFFFF&}did he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:05:01.42,Staff,,0,0,10,,At the height of your popularity, why did you become a painter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.29,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,A painting I did for a "TV Personalities" auction
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:08.41,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,sold at a surprisingly high price.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.12,0:05:14.34,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I thought, "Was my painting alright? Wasn't it too weird?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:19.40,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Jimmy's {\c&H1727D6&}first masterpiece {\c&HFFFFFF&}was sold for 330,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:23.21,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,His work caught the attention of a certain artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.94,0:05:27.97,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I received a letter from Okamoto Taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:29.89,Staff,,0,0,10,,What did the letter say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.24,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,"Go beyond the canvas."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:34.62,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,That was all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.66,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(297,908)}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(297,908)}That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.52,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(297,908)}It's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:41.73,Staff,,0,0,10,,So those words became a strong motivation to become a painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.72,Jimmy,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,852)}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:44.14,Staff,,0,0,10,,Was it not possible to do it along with comedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:44.98,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\pos(723,938)}I tried doing that but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:48.96,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I started struggling with both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:52.21,Title 2 - White,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717,916)\c&H03FFFF&}Comedy {\c&HFFFFFF&}and {\c&H1528D6&}painting {\c&HFFFFFF&}could not coexist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.97,0:05:52.16,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,and so, when choosing which one to go for...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:55.45,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I decided to take a break from show business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:06:00.62,Staff,,0,0,10,,What did Sanma-san tell you after you made your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:04.41,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,"Don't listen to anyone."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:07.66,Staff,,0,0,10,,How did you interpret Sanma-san's advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:12.41,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,That if I listened to what others said, my individuality would die out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:16.77,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,That I shouldn't let go of the good things in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:19.50,Staff,,0,0,10,,Around the time you became a painter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:22.06,Staff,,0,0,10,,you immigrated to Barcelona, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.06,0:06:24.65,Staff,,0,0,10,,Why did you choose to go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:25.53,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(300,842)}You moved to Barcelona?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:29.45,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I visited an art museum in Ueno and fell in love with Picasso...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:34.09,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,so I thought about visiting Picasso's birthplace, Spain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:40.21,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(694.5,204)}That's amazing, I knew there was more \Nto him than just perverted stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:36.96,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,And I ended up going to Barcelona.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.34,Staff,,0,0,10,,Was it hard to adapt to the differences with Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:42.84,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Yeah, being far from Tokyo made me feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:46.80,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,But thankfully, despite being in Spain, in Barcelona...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:52.25,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I was able to quickly find some sex services.
