Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:44.42,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,That it's thanks to him that I can have food on my table.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:49.05,Staff,,0,0,10,,What is the most memorable story you had with Bonchi Osamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.64,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Erm... one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:57.32,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,he told me, "Come to my place, let's drink tonight."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:00.61,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,But something held him up that day so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:04.45,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,he called his wife and told her, "Let Onishi sleep there."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:08.48,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,And then... uh... his wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:12.54,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,she said, "I just got a call from him."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.54,0:16:18.36,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,"He said it was fine for the two of us to sleep before he comes back."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:21.22,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,So I took her up on her offer and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:24.84,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I took off my pants and said, "Let's get started then."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:27.20,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I misunderstood her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.25,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,That's the most memorable...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:33.06,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Ah, that was another dirty story...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:33.04,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(330,314)}That's right, they're banned.
