Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.62,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,It's been 18 hours since the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:41.54,Narrator,,0,0,10,,We've arrived at the period of time that is hardest on the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:44.85,Narrator,,0,0,10,,{\fad(100,100)}How will Jimmy overcome it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:57.89,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Q. How long do you plan to continue as a comedian?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:51.60,Jimmy,,0,0,170,,Until I'm 65.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:52.74,Staff,,0,0,170,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:57.86,Jimmy,,0,0,170,,Because then I'll be able to live off my pension.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:17:13.18,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Q. What do you want to do after you retire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:04.60,Jimmy,,0,0,170,,Look for coffee beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:08.97,Jimmy,,0,0,265,,In retirement, I want to drink good coffee and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:13.17,Jimmy,,0,0,265,,eat castella cake in the afternoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.54,0:17:31.40,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Q. What would you buy for yourself as a reward for your retirement?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:21.06,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(565.5,180)}This guy is just unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.22,Jimmy,,0,0,210,,A walking stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:26.17,Jimmy,,0,0,180,,My knees have started to hurt when I go up and down stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:31.42,Jimmy,,0,0,180,,I'm starting to feel my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:46.72,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Q. A few years ago, what did you change with plastic surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:35.57,Jimmy,,0,0,180,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:35.61,Staff,,0,0,180,,A few years ago you had plastic surgery, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.53,Staff,,0,0,180,,What did you change?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.26,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(172.5,308)}His chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:44.08,Jimmy,,0,0,180,,My chin, it sticked out too much so I pushed it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:57.06,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Q. At this point, why have a plastic surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:57.04,Jimmy,,0,0,180,,At just over 45 years, I thought it was the perfect time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.77,0:17:57.02,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(234,300)}The perfect time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:13.52,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Q. If you were reincarnated, what would you like to become?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:05.98,Jimmy,,0,0,180,,A dog, something like a bulldog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:10.74,Jimmy,,0,0,180,,Someone else will take care of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:13.53,Jimmy,,0,0,180,,and they will fawn over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:16.01,Staff,,0,0,10,,Tape change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:18.61,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Can I take a quick break?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:19.56,Staff,,0,0,10,,Just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:23.56,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Does everyone really do 24 hours straight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.06,Staff,,0,0,10,,{\pos(1117.5,810)}They do... they do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:25.05,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:28.40,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,They don't just record enough and call it a night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:31.50,Staff,,0,0,10,,You're the only one who has complained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:35.01,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,{\alpha&25&\fad(250,100)}It never ends...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:40.20,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,All these questions... they're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:43.25,Staff,,0,0,10,,Well then, let's go to the next question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:50.86,Jimmy,,0,0,5,,Naturally, the 24 hour long interview continues without breaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:55.82,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Along with the sunrise, {\c&H1223C5&}comes trouble!!
