Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.04,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:14.98,Staff,,0,0,10,,{\pos(265.5,802)}How about rice balls?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:16.78,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Sure, I'll make kombu rice balls... yeah...
