Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:29.98,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.02,0:19:31.28,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:34.77,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(240,424)}They just made it, \Nhe needs to let it \Ncool down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:32.00,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.02,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Hot! Hot! Hot! Hot! Hot!
