Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:24.89,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,With his best effort, Jimmy finished making the rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:27.86,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,There are my famous {\c&H0CC40F&}"Square Rice Balls"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.86,0:20:32.10,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,They're neither triangular nor circular, they're square rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:34.60,Staff,,0,0,170,,Thanks for the food.
