Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:41.56,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,They're really good, if I may say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.88,0:20:46.76,Yamazaki,,0,0,0,,{\pos(268.5,360)}They probably don't \Nwant to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:49.20,Staff,,0,0,10,,What do you think Kojima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.78,Staff,,0,0,10,,It's a ball of goo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:53.26,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(307.5,304)}He used too much water.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.32,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Well, at least it's light on the stomach...
