Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:11.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's a little over 9 AM and there's only one hour left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.61,Narrator,,0,0,10,,Alright, this is the last spurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:17.76,Narrator,,0,0,10,,Please tell us about the angriest moment in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:22.00,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Um... I had a wound back here and it became a bald spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:27.37,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I was in the bullet train when this old guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:33.28,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,started poking my bald spot with a toothpick, so I got angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:36.00,Staff,,0,0,10,,In what way did you lose your temper?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.66,0:21:38.69,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I told him, "Hey! I'll tell the conductor and {\alpha&FF&}have him change my seat!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:41.05,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I told him, "Hey! I'll tell the conductor and have him change my seat!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.12,0:21:45.24,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,And I did so they changed my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:48.65,Staff,,0,0,10,,Which animal would you compare yourself to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:50.33,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,An animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.33,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,an orangutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:54.25,Staff,,0,0,10,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.60,0:21:56.81,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Fear of extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.12,Staff,,0,0,10,,Fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:22:03.40,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,Yes, about being on the edge of extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:08.00,Staff,,0,0,10,,What have these last 24 hours made you realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:12.81,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I think I said too many perverted things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:13.22,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(210,308)}Ah, he's aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:16.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(210,308)}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.33,0:22:17.74,Jimmy,,0,0,10,,I became aware that I'm pretty much {\c&HA864F1&}masturbation-man{\c&HFFFFFF&}.
